ficient project implementation, M&amp;E of results, and a consistent and effective approach to capacity building. Nutrition, gender, and climate smart agriculture considerations are mainstreamed throughout all components.</p>\r\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner#][/kc_row_inner#][/kc_column_inner][/kc_row_inner][kc_row_inner _id=\"877078\" cols_gap=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`479`:{`box`:{`margin|`:`30px inherit 30px inherit`}},`any`:{`box`:{`margin|`:`50px inherit 50px inherit`}}}}\"][kc_column_inner width=\"50%\" _id=\"760468\"][kc_row_inner# _id=\"650899\" cols_gap=\"{`kc-css`:{}}\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`479`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit 0px inherit inherit`}},`767`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit 0px inherit inherit`}},`999`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit 0px inherit inherit`}},`any`:{`typography`:{`text-align|`:`right`},`box`:{`padding|`:`35px 30px inherit inherit`}}}}\" row_class=\"video-info video-border-two\"][kc_column_inner# width=\"100%\" _id=\"165682\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`box`:{`float|`:`right`}}}}\"][kc_title text=\"SGVscCBVcyBBIExpdHRsZQ==\" _id=\"728244\" type=\"h3\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`title-style`:{`font-family|+.kc_title,.kc_title,.kc_title a.kc_title_link`:`Roboto Slab`,`font-size|+.kc_title,.kc_title,.kc_title a.kc_title_link`:`30px`}}}}\"][kc_column_text _id=\"921254\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`any`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit inherit inherit 27px`}}}}\"]<p> There are many variations of passages charity charity hub charity wordpress theme donate donations fundraising theme fundraising ngo non profit non profit theme fund organization social volunteer charity charity causes</p>\r\n[/kc_column_text][/kc_column_inner#][/kc_row_inner#][/kc_column_inner][kc_column_inner width=\"50%\" _id=\"935148\" css_custom=\"{`kc-css`:{`479`:{`box`:{`padding|`:`inherit inherit inherit 15px`}}}}\"][vorosa_video_popup video_popup_random_key=\"57461\" source=\"youtube\" video_link=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6tfFRD0enV0\" video